  "description": {
    "zh": "说到抢先行动……\n在你完成上一次的任务后，我便派了一些人去那里，结果发现那里满是Scav和PMC，用“战区”来形容都显得太轻松了，虽然确实如此。\n\n好吧，有兴趣再接一单任务吗？我需要你去清理总部周围的任何人，我们需要转移人们对这个地方的注意力，不能让他们趁机拿走我们需要的东西。",
    "en": "Speaking of people getting curious...\nI sent out a few people out there after you came back from your last job and the place was filled with bandits and operators, a \"warzone\" would be an understatement even tho it's describing it pretty well.\n\nWell, interested in another job? You'll need to clear out the HQ grounds from anyone you can see, we need to move away the attention from this place, we can't let people get away with more things that we need."
  },
